{"id":1169,"date":"2018-01-22T07:14:15","date_gmt":"2018-01-22T07:14:15","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=1169"},"modified":"2021-02-27T09:44:37","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T09:44:37","slug":"3-cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/3-cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat\/","title":{"rendered":"3 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">B\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ri\u00eang cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, tuy nhi\u00ean sau th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ef1 m\u00ecnh l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 v\u1eabn hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3. D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ed9 sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t BYZAN gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u cho qu\u00fd v\u1ecb tham kh\u1ea3o.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gh\u1ebf sofa v\u1ea3i n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n<\/strong><\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">V\u1ebft b\u1ea9n tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf sofa v\u1ea3i n\u1ec9 c\u00f3 nh\u1ec1u lo\u1ea1i kh\u00e1c nhau nh\u01b0 m\u1ef1c b\u00fat bi, n\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e0 ph\u00ea, k\u1eb9o b\u00e1nh tr\u1ebb nh\u1ecf l\u00e0m d\u00ednh l\u00ean gh\u1ebf\u2026\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n n\u00e0y, ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n nh\u01b0 m\u1ef1c b\u00fat bi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch sau: l\u1ea5y m\u1ed9t \u00edt c\u1ed3n nh\u1ecf l\u00ean v\u1ebft m\u1ef1c r\u1ed3i d\u00f9ng gi\u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5m h\u00fat cao cho m\u1ef1c th\u1ea5m h\u1ebft sang gi\u1ea5y, l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 v\u1eady nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n sau \u0111\u00f3 gi\u1eb7t v\u1ea3i b\u1ecdc gh\u1ebf sofa v\u1edbi x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng cho s\u1ea1ch h\u1eb3n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 d\u1ec5 l\u00e0m.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1170\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"860\" height=\"595\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat-2.jpg 860w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat-2-300x208.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat-2-768x531.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n cho b\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">M\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch n\u1eefa \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 mua s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m chuy\u00ean d\u00f9ng cho t\u1ea9y r\u1eeda gh\u1ebf sopha nh\u01b0 b\u1ed9t sumo (lo\u1ea1i n\u00e0y tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh cao). Ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u1ecd x\u1ecbt t\u1ea9y d\u00f9ng trong n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t xe h\u01a1i, x\u1ecbt l\u00ean v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n r\u1ed3i \u0111\u00ea 2 \u2013 3 ph\u00fat sau \u0111\u00f3 d\u00f9ng kh\u0103n \u1ea9m lau l\u00ean v\u1ebft b\u1ea9n \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng d\u00f9ng m\u00e1y s\u1ea5y t\u00f3c \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m kh\u00f4.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u00e1m<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 b\u00e1m b\u1ee5i, ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf b\u1ee5i b\u00e1m tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf sofa theo c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch sau:<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc h\u1ebft b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y l\u1ed9t v\u1ecf c\u00e1c t\u1ea5m n\u1ec7m l\u00f3t v\u00e0 gi\u1eb7t v\u1edbi x\u00e0 b\u00f4ng, h\u00e3y ng\u00e2m v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u00e0 ph\u00f2ng \u1ea5m tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u1eeda ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1eb7t.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">D\u00f9ng m\u00e1y h\u00fat b\u1ee5i c\u1ea7m tay h\u00fat s\u1ea1ch b\u1ee5i \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i tr\u00ean gh\u1ebf sofa. C\u00f2n n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u00e1y h\u00fat b\u1ee5i h\u00e3y d\u00f9ng t\u1ea5m kh\u0103n \u1ea9m tr\u1ea3i tr\u00ean b\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t gh\u1ebf v\u00e0 l\u1ea5y g\u1eady \u0111\u1eadp, b\u1ee5i b\u1ea9n s\u1ebd b\u00e1m v\u00e0o kh\u0103n. C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.<\/span><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-1171\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"860\" height=\"484\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat.jpg 860w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat-300x169.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2018\/01\/cach-lam-sach-sofa-ni-tai-nha-don-gian-nhat-768x432.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px\" \/>D\u00f9ng m\u00e1y h\u00fat b\u1ee5i lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf nh\u1eefng b\u1ee5i b\u00e1m tr\u00ean sofa n\u1ec9<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 b\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c kh\u1eed m\u00f9i<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">\u0110\u1ec3 b\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n m\u00f9i h\u00f4i b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 nh\u1ecf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ecdt h\u01b0\u01a1ng li\u1ec7u y\u00eau th\u00edch v\u00e0o que b\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 qu\u1ea5n l\u1ea1i trong chi\u1ebfc kh\u0103n v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7t sau g\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ec7m gh\u1ebf sofa. D\u00f9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ecbt kh\u1eed m\u00f9i chuy\u00ean d\u1ee5ng cho c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i v\u1ea3i v\u00e0 th\u1ea3m hay khi gi\u1eb7t b\u1ea1n ng\u00e2m n\u01b0\u1edbc x\u1ea3 v\u1ea3i c\u00f3 h\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u01a1m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u1eed m\u00f9i h\u00f4i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/span><br \/>\n<span style=\"font-family: tahoma, arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Tr\u00ean \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 t\u1ea1i nh\u00e0 m\u00e0 N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t BYZAN gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ebfn qu\u00fd v\u1ecb. H\u00e3y tham kh\u1ea3o v\u00e0 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng ngay cho b\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa nh\u00e0 m\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n nh\u00e9!<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>B\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa n\u1ec9 mang l\u1ea1i v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p ri\u00eang cho kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n, tuy nhi\u00ean sau th\u1eddi gian s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng n\u00f3 s\u1ebd b\u1ecb b\u1ea9n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n \u0111\u1eb9p nh\u01b0 m\u1edbi. Vi\u1ec7c l\u00e0m s\u1ea1ch b\u1ed9 gh\u1ebf sofa l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ed1n k\u00e9m, b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":822,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-1169","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1169","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1169"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1169\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/822"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1169"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1169"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1169"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}